      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0007": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0007",
        "Text": "让自己的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1503>上升的攻击称为「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1302>」\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1302>命中敌方会使<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1503>量表上升，到达一定的值就会让自己的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1401>提升\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1503>升级的话，会强化<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1307>并增加伤害"
      },
