      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0008": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0008",
        "Text": "连续输入<img id=\"NormalAttack_1\"/>可以使出连结<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1302>和<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1307>的连击「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1301>」\n只有在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1503>足以发动<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1307>的状态下\n使出「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1301>」会让最后的招式变化为<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1307>"
