      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0102": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0102",
        "Text": "和伙伴角色攻击同一个敌人\n或是攻击正在攻击伙伴的敌人会产生「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1402>」\n出现奖励后可以获得追加的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1505>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0103": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0103",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1314>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0103": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0103",
        "Text": "用<img id=\"MoveDown\"/>＋<img id=\"NormalAttack_1\"/>可以使出「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1313>」\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1313>无法<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1409>，击中敌方后，敌方就会变成特殊的受创状态\n在敌方的受创状态期间，伙伴的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1301>或<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1302>击中敌方\n会发动和伙伴的合作攻击「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1314>」\n\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1314>发动的话自己和伙伴的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1401>会上升\n并且可以对敌方造成大量伤害"
