        "Text": "让<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1401>变成最大"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_TASK_MESSAGE_0202": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_TASK_MESSAGE_0202",
        "Text": "让<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1315>成功"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_TASK_COMMAND_LABEL_0202": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_TASK_COMMAND_LABEL_0202",
        "Text": "<img id=\"Guard\"/>＋<img id=\"CursedEnergyAttack_2\"/>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0201": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0201",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0201": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0201",
        "Text": "一部分角色的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1315>可以发动<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>\n\n<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>成功的话，能将敌方和我方拉进自己的领域\n在领域内自己的能力会提升，对敌方造成妨碍效果和大伤害\n可以在有利的状态展开<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0202": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0202",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0202": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0202",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>会因以下任一原因解除\n时间经过、发动者被<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1418>、有别的<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>覆盖过原本的领域\n另外，也有从展开后攻击，一连串进行到解除的类型存在\n\n一部分角色在<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0006>解除后的一定时间内\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1307>可能会受到限制，需要注意"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0301": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_LABEL_0301",
        "Text": "关于适应"
      },
      "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0301": {
        "ID": "TUT_INGAME_MESSAGE_0301",
        "Text": "魔虚罗有「适应」对手攻击，并使其无效的能力。\n击败魔虚罗的咒力技会被适应，之后无法造成损伤。\n招式如果被适应了，与招式对应的法阵图示就会亮起。\n\n觉醒技可以造成损伤。\n最后就用这招式打败魔虚罗吧。"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0001": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0001",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1001>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0001": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0001",
        "Text": "在「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1001>」可以体验<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_0001>的故事\n\n・<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1103>…\n　再次体验<GLO=GLS_UNIQUE_WORDS_0001>等人的战斗记录\n・<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1206>…\n　确认各角色的关系性"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0101": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0101",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1103>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0101": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0101",
        "Text": "在这里可以照时间顺序选择任务体验故事\n\n根据任务将有特殊的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1601>条件\n或「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1817>」这种课题的类型\n任务细节可按下<img id=\"PopupMenu_2\"/>确认"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0102": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0102",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1206>的进行"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0102": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0102",
        "Text": "推进<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1103>会让<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1206>的角色开放\n以及角色之间的关系进展\n不时确认看看吧\n\n也可透过按下<img id=\"PopupMenu_1\"/>移动到<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1206>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0201": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0201",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1206>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0201": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0201",
        "Text": "在这里可以确认角色之间的关系性\n进行<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1103>会让角色之间的「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1105>」上升\n可以获得报酬，或是观看开放的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1706>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0301": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0301",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1002>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0301_10": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0301_10",
        "Text": "在这里可以连上网络进行线上对战\n\n・<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1102>…\n　可以轻松对战\n・<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1101>…\n　与实力相近的玩家们对战"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0301_20": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0301_20",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1101>与实力相近的玩家们对战\n依对战结果和分数会让「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1901>」变动\n也可以依累计分数获得报酬\n详情可在「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1208>」确认"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0401": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0401",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1003>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0401_10": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0401_10",
        "Text": "在这里可以连上网络在线上和玩家协力\n以特殊规则进行与敌方的连续<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>\n\n・<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1801>…\n　可以和玩家协力\n　进行每次游玩会变化，以「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1815>」构成的连续<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>\n　达成「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1817>」的条件并打倒敌人获得高分吧\n　另外也有设有特殊胜败条件的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0401_20": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0401_20",
        "Text": "・<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1802>…\n　敌人比<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1801>更强的模式\n　请以完全攻略为目标"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0402": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0402",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1003>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0402": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0402",
        "Text": "先游玩「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1801>」，体验模式的流程吧\n第一次将是线下游玩\n\n另外，第一次以后只要选择「一个人游玩」\n就可以在线下游玩"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0403": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0403",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1818>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0403": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0403",
        "Text": "在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1801>只要游玩「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1818>」就会变动\n当<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1818>上升，<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1801>的难度\n和<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>的构成也会阶段性变化\n协力的玩家将会优先配对<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1818>相近的玩家\n\n出击时可以任意设定<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1818>以调整难度\n※如果降低后出击，<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1818>上限不会提升"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0404": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0404",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>/<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1804>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0404": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0404",
        "Text": "另外，在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1003>\n可以「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1804>」特殊的「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>道具」或角色而达到强化\n游玩<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1801>、<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1802>以获得<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1812>\n强化角色吧\n\n强化后会比较容易攻略困难的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0501": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0501",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0501": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0501",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1007>购买的道具的角色可以强化角色\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>最多可装3个，<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1804>角色就会开放栏位\n但是无法<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>复数个同一类型的道具\n\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>道具有可以永久<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>的类型\n和发挥一次效果就会消失的各种种类\n另外，游玩<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1003>可能会让<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1007>陈列新的道具"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0502": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0502",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1804>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0502": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0502",
        "Text": "可以使用游玩<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1801>、<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1802>获得的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1812>\n来提升角色的LV\nLV提升会强化数值，<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1805>栏位会被开放\n\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1812>是游玩任何角色都会共同累计，可以自由分配"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0601": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0601",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1809>的选择"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0601": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0601",
        "Text": "在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1003>可以对自己设定「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1809>」\n设定<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1809>将会限制行动或数值等，而强化其他能力\n\n在设定<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1809>的状态下通关任务，可以追加获得<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1819>点数"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0701": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0701",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1831>可以做的事"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0701": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0701",
        "Text": "在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1831>画面可以为了准备下个任务\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1819>「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1422>」或个别的「<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1502>」\n各个<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1819>都需要点数\n点数是由玩家各自持有，好好运用<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1819>吧\n\n这个<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1819>点数可在任务通关时获得\n另外，设定<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1809>的状态下通关任务，可以追加获得点数"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0801": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0801",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1005>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0801": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0801",
        "Text": "在这里可以自由设定角色和规则来游玩<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>\n\n・角色设定…\n　可以设定我方和对手的角色选择及强度\n\n・玩家设定…\n　可以设定特殊项目\n\n・<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>设定…\n　可以设定关卡限制时间、<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1503>等规则"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0901": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_0901",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1004>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0901_10": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0901_10",
        "Text": "在这里可以连接网络在线上建立大厅\n与<DYN=FRIEND_WORD>和陌生人等固定成员游玩\n\n・建立大厅…以房主身分建立大厅\n　可以变更游玩方式和招募文来募集风格契合的玩家\n\n・寻找大厅…参加已建立的大厅\n　搜寻<DYN=FRIEND_WORD>或ID可以直接参加特定大厅"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0901_20": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_0901_20",
        "Text": "・角色选择…\n　选择在大厅操作的角色\n　在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>可以选择别的角色，以喜欢的角色参加大厅吧！"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1001": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1001",
        "Text": "大厅房主可以做的事"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1001_10": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1001_10",
        "Text": "大厅房主长按<img id=\"BattlePause\"/>开始<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>\n成员到齐以后就开始吧"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1001_20": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1001_20",
        "Text": "另外，可以用<img id=\"BattlePause\"/>打开选单做以下动作\n\n・出击模式的设定…\n　可以变更大厅成员游玩的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>模式\n\n・玩家的踢除…\n　可以从大厅踢除玩家\n　这项操作要从大厅情报进行"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1002": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1002",
        "Text": "在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1004>可以做的事"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1002_10": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1002_10",
        "Text": "在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1004>可以做以下动作\n\n・定型<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1416>…\n　用<img id=\"ChatUp\"/><img id=\"ChatDown\"/><img id=\"ChatLeft\"/><img id=\"ChatRight\"/>进行定型<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1416>\n\n・不显示UI…\n　可用<img id=\"WidgetDispSwitch\"/>切换UI的显示／不显示"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1002_20": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1002_20",
        "Text": "・切换视角模式…\n　可以切换成能用<img id=\"CameraUp\"/><img id=\"CameraDown\"/><img id=\"CameraLeft\"/><img id=\"CameraRight\"/>自由移动视角的模式\n\n大厅房主开始<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>\n而要退出大厅可用<img id=\"BattlePause\"/>显示选单"
      },
