        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1101",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1007>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1101": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1101",
        "Text": "在这里可以使用从<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>等获得的<img id=\"Money_0001\"/><GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_2103>\n购买<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_2217>或<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1207>的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202>道具\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1003><GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>专用道具等\n\n一部分道具为达成条件后可以购买"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1102": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_LABEL_1102",
        "Text": "关于<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_2102>"
      },
      "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1102": {
        "ID": "TUT_OUTGAME_MESSAGE_1102",
        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_2102>是可以<GLO=GLS_NAME_MAP_00>获得<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1007>道具的道具\n\n※不包含有开放条件的道具\n※如果抽中已取得，或是数量超过上限数量的道具\n将转变为<img id=\"Money_0001\"/><GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_2103>"
