        "Text": "可以照喜好<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202><GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1207>\n\n个别的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202>道具可透过游玩<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>或是在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1007>购买来获得"
