        "Text": "可以照喜好<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202><GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>中的定型<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1416>\n\n不同角色可以个别设定\n<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202>适合游玩风格的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1416>吧"
