        "Text": "<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202>VS姿势和<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>语音\n\n个别的<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1202>道具可透过游玩<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1813>或是在<GLO=GLS_GAME_WORDS_1007>购买而获得"
